Sharing model dataÔÉÅ

To package model data for sharing:

  1. Review configuration settings in Scripts\share\standard_data\hand\config.yaml and update them if necessary.

  2. Execute Scripts\share\standard_data\run.cmd to run standard_data.py.

Data read from the containing trip-based model project directory will be written to Scripts\share\standard_data\output.

Templates for the Data User Guide in Scripts\share\standard_data\hand may be edited as needed.

  • data_user_guide_md.txt - Markdown template used for content

  • data_user_guide_html.txt - HTML template used for styling
